[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0505","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0505.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0304","title":"BSD mmap 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"BSD 系统中 mmap 函数存在权限检查缺陷，属于 kmem 组的本地攻击者可通过操作设备文件实现对内核内存的未授权读写访问，进而提升至 root 权限。该漏洞影响多种 BSD 衍生操作系统，攻击者需先获得本地低权限账户并属于 kmem 组方可利用，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0304"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.750","remediation":"建议立即升级至 FreeBSD 3.0 及以上已修复版本，或应用对应 BSD 厂商的安全补丁。严格限制 kmem 组成员仅限 root 用户，将 /dev/mem 和 /dev/kmem 权限设为 600（仅 root 可读写）。可通过 sysctl -w security.bsd.mmap_of_physmem=0 禁止物理内存映射，并配置内核参数 kern.randompid=1 增强 ASLR 缓解效果。移除不必要的 kmem 组用户，避免被用于内核内存访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0304"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0505.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0441","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0441.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0256","title":"War-FTPD 1.65 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"War-FTPD 1.65 在处理用户登录时的密码字段存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务发送超长的密码字符串触发基于栈的缓冲区溢出，导致服务器进程崩溃或在目标系统上执行任意代码。Metasploit 框架已集成该漏洞的利用模块，攻击门槛较低。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0256"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.867","remediation":"升级 War-FTPD 至 1.82.00 RC 或更高版本，该版本已修复 Username/Password 栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。如该软件已停止维护，建议迁移至主动维护的 FTP 服务器（如 vsftpd、ProFTPD），并在防火墙限制对 FTP 服务的访问来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/875","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/16706","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0256.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0256.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0256","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0256.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0256.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-836r-gprf-7h7h/GHSA-836r-gprf-7h7h.json","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/DDI_warftpd_user_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/openctibr/threatFeeds/blob/3455d6adfb8ec0cc7fbb444ace396770ca5ca6c0/ExploitableVulnerabilitiesFeed.txt","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0441.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0205","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0205.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0087","title":"IBM AIX Telnet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.1/4.2/4.3 版本 Telnet 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向目标系统发送特制的 Telnet 协议数据包，触发服务进程异常崩溃，导致系统完全冻结，合法用户无法登录或访问服务器资源。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.1/4.2/4.3 版本，攻击门槛低，危害中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0087"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.180","remediation":"建议升级 AIX 至 4.3.3 或更高版本，IBM 已在后续维护版本中修复此问题。如无法升级，可在 inetd.conf 中注释 telnet 行并使用 refresh -s inetd 生效，改用 SSH 替代 telnet 服务，同时在防火墙上限制对 23/TCP 端口的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0087","https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0087","http://www.osvdb.org/7992"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0205.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0448","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0448.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0264","title":"Miva htmlscript 2.x 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Miva htmlscript 2.x 中的 CGI 程序存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过特制的 URL 路径参数，绕过路径限制访问服务器上的任意文件（如密码文件、配置文件等）。该漏洞影响 htmlscript 2.x 版本，攻击者只需发送 HTTP 请求即可利用，危害等级中等，建议升级至最新版本或禁用该 CGI 程序。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0264"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.847","remediation":"升级 Miva htmlscript 至 3.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复目录遍历问题；如产品已停止维护，应立即从 Web 服务器 cgi-bin 目录中移除 htmlscript CGI 程序。临时缓解措施：在 Apache/Nginx 层面配置规则拦截包含 \"../\" 的 URL 请求，或通过 .htaccess 限制对 htmlscript 脚本的访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0264","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20434","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0264.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0264","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0264.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0264.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h676-3v8p-5vwf/GHSA-h676-3v8p-5vwf.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0264.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.829","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2d13d37d-5c85-422a-bd4e-7e51f93842cc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0448.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0271","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0271.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0125","title":"SGI IRIX mailx 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 系统中的 mailx 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，由于程序对用户输入的数据长度缺乏充分校验，当攻击者向 mailx 程序传入特制的超长参数时，可触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致程序异常崩溃。本地攻击者可利用该漏洞实现权限提升，获取 root 权限。该漏洞同样影响 RedHat Linux 4.2 和 Solaris 2.6 系统。CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0125"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.563","remediation":"SGI IRIX 用户请安装 SGI 安全公告 19980605-01-PX 提供的 mailx 补丁；RedHat Linux 4.2 用户升级 mailx 到已修复版本；Solaris 2.6 用户安装 Sun 官方 mailx 补丁。临时缓解措施可移除 mailx 的 setuid 位：chmod u-s /bin/mailx。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19312","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0125.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0125","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0125.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0125.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0125.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0