itle":"多厂商 CDE dtappgather 未授权权限提升漏洞","description":"CDE 桌面环境中的 dtappgather 程序存在文件权限更改漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该程序获取非授权提权访问权限或导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 10.20/11.0、IBM AIX 4.3、SCO Unixware 7.0 及 Sun Solaris 2.6 等操作系统，攻击者通过向 dtappgather 发送特制请求即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0014"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:21.147","remediation":"联系各操作系统厂商获取对应补丁：HP-UX 安装 PHSS_15068 补丁包，AIX 安装 IY66454 更新，移除 dtappgather 程序的 setuid 权限（chmod 0555 /usr/dt/bin/dtappgather），或在无需 CDE 环境时卸载 dtlogin/CDE 套件以彻底消除攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/185","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9801-075","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19108","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0014.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0014","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0014.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0014.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0014.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wgf5-r6hp-p33g/GHSA-wgf5-r6hp-p33g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0d95d209-999a-431c-9c33-fdcc7f8c9c24.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0045.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0045.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0045.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0457","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0457.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0271","title":"Progressive Networks Real Video Server 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Progressive Networks Real Video server（pnserver）存在远程拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过发送特制数据包触发该漏洞，导致服务崩溃，影响正常视频流服务。该漏洞利用难度较低，攻击条件简单，但仅影响服务可用性，不会导致数据泄露或权限提升。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0271"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.730","remediation":"建议立即升级至已修复该漏洞的 Progressive Networks RealVideo Server 最新版本，或从网络层面在防火墙上限制对 pnserver 服务端口（默认 TCP 7070）的访问来源，仅允许可信 IP 连接。由于该产品已长期停止维护，强烈建议迁移至现代受支持的流媒体服务器（如 Wowza Streaming Engine 或 Nginx-RTMP）以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0271","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0271.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0271","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0271.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0271.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0271.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6vw2-j8x2-pj9j/GHSA-6vw2-j8x2-pj9j.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/P/pnserver.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82096/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0271.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0457.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0203","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0203.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0086","title":"IBM AIX routed 远程敏感文件修改漏洞","description":"AIX 系统中的 routed 路由守护进程存在访问控制缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的 RIP 路由协议报文，利用该漏洞可修改系统敏感文件，从而获得非授权访问权限或造成系统配置被篡改。该漏洞影响 AIX 操作系统的 routed 服务，攻击者可通过伪造路由更新实施攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0086"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.940","remediation":"升级 AIX 至受支持的最新版本（7.2 TL5/7.3 及以上），该版本已不再使用存在漏洞的 routed 实现。若无法升级，立即停止 routed 服务（`stopsrc -s routed`）并在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释相关行，同时在防火墙侧阻断外部对 UDP 520 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0086"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0203.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0767","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0767.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0513","title":"Linux Kernel 2.0/2.1 ICMP Smurf 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.0/2.1 存在 ICMP Smurf 拒绝服务漏洞。攻击者通过向网络广播地址发送源地址伪造为目标的 ICMP Echo 请求数据包，导致该网络中所有主机同时向目标发送大量 ICMP 应答，形成流量放大攻击，造成目标系统网络带宽耗尽而拒绝服务。该攻击需要目标网络允许定向广播包且主机数较多，效果显著，影响 Linux 及多种 UNIX 系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0513"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-01-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:33.307","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.2 及以上版本，或设置内核参数 `net.ipv4.icmp_echo_ignore_broadcasts=1` 以及 `net.ipv4.icmp_ignore_bogus_error_responses=1`；在边界路由器上执行 `no ip directed-broadcast` 禁用定向广播转发，并在网络出口过滤 ICMP 回显请求。若为 Cisco 设备，在接口配置 `ip directed-broadcast` 为 `disabled`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0513","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19117"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0767.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0560","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0560.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0341","title":"Debian Linux deliver 邮件程序本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Debian Linux 系统中的 mail 程序 \"deliver\" 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该漏洞通过精心构造的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取系统 root 权限。该漏洞需攻击者拥有本地访问权限，危害等级高，影响 Debian Linux 系统。建议及时安装厂商发布的安全补丁进行修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0341"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:11.357","remediation":"升级 Linux 发行版至至少 Debian 3.0（Woody）以上版本，该版本已移除有漏洞的 deliver 程序，改用更安全的邮件传输代理。如因特殊原因仍使用 deliver，立即将其 SUID 权限移除（chmod u-s /usr/bin/deliver），并迁移至 exim 或 postfix 等现代 MTA。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0341"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0560.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0547","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0547.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0331","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0/4.0.1 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可构造特制网页或 URL，诱使用户访问后触发缓冲区溢出，导致浏览器崩溃或执行任意代码。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。该漏洞影响 Windows 平台上 IE 4.0 及 4.0.1 版本，攻击复杂度低且无需认证，仅需用户交互即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0331"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.197","remediation":"立即升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 及以上版本，Microsoft 已在 IE 5.0 中修复此缓冲区溢出漏洞。对于当前仍在使用的旧系统，应停止使用 IE 4.0 并迁移至 Microsoft Edge 或 Chrome 等受支持的现代浏览器。如无法升级浏览器，可通过防火墙限制受感染主机对外部恶意服务器的 80/443 端口访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0331","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0331.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0331","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0331.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0331.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/057c97aa60eb958a2d272c7164e35c156db63b6c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pjph-v9v4-hggg/GHSA-pjph-v9v4-hggg.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0331.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0547.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0547.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0487","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0487.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0293","title":"Cisco IOS AAA认证远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 系统的 AAA（认证、授权、审计）认证模块存在授权绕过漏洞，远程攻击者可在未获得合法凭据的情况下绕过认证机制，直接执行任意命令。该漏洞影响多款 Cisco 路由器及交换机设备，攻击者利用该漏洞可完全控制目标设备，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。目前建议用户升级至修复版本或配置严格的访问控制列表进行缓解。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0293"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.380","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至修复该漏洞的版本（如 11.x 及以上已打补丁版本），启用 `aaa new-model` 并配置 TACACS+ 或 RADIUS 服务器进行认证授权，避免仅依赖本地 enable 密码。在 `aaa authentication` 和 `aaa authorization` 命令中指定 `group tacacs+` 作为首选方法，禁止未认证用户通过 AAA 接口执行命令。如无法升级，在受控接口上配置 ACL 限制仅允许可信管理源 IP 访问设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0293","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0293.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0293","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0293.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0293.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0293.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-wmmp-2f22-959m/GHSA-wmmp-2f22-959m.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2007/CVE-2007-4632.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82266/info.html","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/5c36feecacaa0eef96caef76eb433e2bf57c7235/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0293.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0487.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0473","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0473.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0284","title":"Microsoft Exchange Server SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange Server 4.0/5.0 及 Alt-N MDaemon 等 NT 邮件服务器的 SMTP 服务存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务器发送超长参数的 HELO 命令，可触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，仅需构造特制 SMTP 数据包即可实施攻击，影响范围广泛。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0284"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.237","remediation":"升级 Microsoft Exchange Server 至 5.5 或更高版本，该版本已修复 SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出问题。对于 Alt-N MDaemon，升级至 2.72 或更高版本。如无法升级，在防火墙层面限制对 SMTP 端口（25/TCP）的访问来源，仅允许可信邮件服务器连接，并部署入侵检测规则拦截超长 HELO 参数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0284","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/23113","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0284.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0284","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0284.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0284.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v64w-xq9r-xp4x/GHSA-v64w-xq9r-xp4x.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0284.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/M/mdaemon.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x9000/8622/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0473.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0473.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0473.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0465","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0465.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0279","title":"Excite Excite for Web Servers 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Excite for Web Servers（EWS）存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向服务提交包含 shell 元字符（如管道符、分号）的恶意请求，在服务进程中执行任意操作系统命令。该漏洞源于 EWS 对用户输入过滤不严，未正确处理 shell 特殊字符，导致攻击者可远程控制目标服务器。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0279"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.717","remediation":"Excite for Web Servers (EWS) 已停止维护多年，无官方补丁。建议立即迁移至现代 Web 服务器（如 Apache/Nginx）替代 EWS。如无法立即迁移，在反向代理层过滤用户输入中的 shell 元字符（; | ` $ &）、严格限制 CGI 参数、并对 Web 服务目录实施最小权限访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0279","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea